name: Meditation Rabbit #10
description:
‘Meditation Rabbit’ is a collection of collectible rabbits created by Alexis Olin.

It’s powerful artworks to cope with the hectic pace of modern life and empowers people to experience their lives to its fullest potential. Bring health, dynamism, prosperity and well being.

“Life is one long insane trip. Some rabbits just have better directions.”

On permanent display at the digital part of Louvre, Paris since 2021.
